{"tid":723283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"dllm 可口可樂","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T10:02:08.000Z","uid":30084,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4a096d2a1e7e716acc9a5b7a10244239fe8392","tid":723283,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>話說 可樂出左個活動 掃qr 就有獎抽<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170041_00b63c9f0beaf32ffb20c8dbef3372a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170041_00b63c9f0beaf32ffb20c8dbef3372a7.png&h=895b9806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁好喇飲完就拆個扣出黎掃</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170229_14ca165036f891926ec1bff483083453.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170229_14ca165036f891926ec1bff483083453.png&h=29e9c40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你地都知電話影相 有最短對焦距離，個扣細到咁，近又唔得 遠又太細 我屌你老母 掃極都掃唔到</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170321_037ac48af1ab6a8627238476153f71b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170321_037ac48af1ab6a8627238476153f71b9.png&h=cb6307f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170338_5ed27716faa99dbb50dfa35d1db5594f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170338_5ed27716faa99dbb50dfa35d1db5594f.png&h=92ca41cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170533_f6df96f9f210d2c5fb1b64461512869c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170533_f6df96f9f210d2c5fb1b64461512869c.png&h=993b8fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>之後我諗到計 單反開macro 放大個qr 再用手機掃</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170634_98a78223735140c1cf8067c0578e4e4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170634_98a78223735140c1cf8067c0578e4e4a.png&h=589c05f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我屌你老母 都係唔得呀，你唔好撚再細d</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/170801_ba0bfa669c66225928426508e4ca08bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F170801_ba0bfa669c66225928426508e4ca08bc.png&h=096e5d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我放棄 有邊位巴打掃到 就送俾你地</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/171004_cea34beb95bf85d99fa5553eec85a0b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F171004_cea34beb95bf85d99fa5553eec85a0b4.png&h=48e90cb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97b802c4c7fd7ce5b4ea071dcb9215b35240056a","tid":723283,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"放棄左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077b0a0267f2e371a839d4ff5292d30824cd2272","tid":723283,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/755/d83/755d834d9f527f8345237bfa8075a6c688d35e68_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F755%2Fd83%2F755d834d9f527f8345237bfa8075a6c688d35e68_n.png&h=b14b435d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a8768c13016b24061d8634a1a11da0d6b3e691f","tid":723283,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"買過4次4次都掃到   中左兩罐免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b60346fcdbc15b5f